<h1>Japan</h1>
    <p>Japan is a country in Asia. It's usually known as a country where animation is famous</p>
    <p>Japan is an island country in East Asia. It is located in the Pacific Ocean off the northeast coast of the Asian mainland, and is bordered on the west by the Sea of Japan and extends from the Sea of Okhotsk in the north to the East China Sea in the south</p>